 B.S. or M.S. in Computer Science or related field (or similar work experience); 



 You have interacted with many dapps via metamask; 



 Experience working with a highly distributed Engineering running a SCRUM team with continuous integration, automated testing; 



 An appetite for software design tempered with an understanding of practical trade-offs in development (lean, MVP); 



 Amazon AWS, CDN's, Heroku and scaling assets to worldwide users under high loads. 



